<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Richard David Bach</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Born</th>
<td>23 June 1936 <span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1936-06-23</span>)</span> <span class="noprint">(age&#160;72)</span><br />
